üåª Good morning friends, how is your day going?
üì∫ Are you looking for relaxation, positivity and energy for the new day? This will be the perfect place for you!

üìå The golden hues of autumn wrap the cafe in a warm embrace as the gentle notes of jazz piano fill the air. Outside, the lake reflects the colors of the season ‚Äî amber leaves drifting across the water beneath the fading sunset. Inside, the soft crackle of the fireplace and the glow of candlelight create a peaceful sanctuary, perfect for quiet reflection and a cup of coffee. Every corner tells a story ‚Äî the books on the shelves, the pumpkins by the hearth, and the inviting table set for two by the lakeside. The music flows like the calm ripples of the water, carrying the heart to a place of serenity and warmth. It‚Äôs a moment suspended in time, where sound and stillness blend in perfect harmony.

üçÇ As twilight deepens, the cafe becomes a haven of calm and comfort. The soft rhythm of the piano invites you to slow down, breathe deeply, and savor the beauty of autumn ‚Äî a season made for cozy nights, glowing fires, and soulful melodies.

title: Evanescence - My Immortal (Official HD Music Video)
description:
Official HD music video for ‚ÄúMy Immortal,‚Äù taken from the band‚Äôs multi-platinum debut Fallen.

Evanescence are celebrating the 20th anniversary of Fallen with a series of special reissues via Craft Recordings. 

Details/order: https://found.ee/fallen20 

Available on Deluxe 2-LP, 2-CD, and Digital ‚Äî as well as a Super Deluxe Edition collector‚Äôs box set ‚Äî Fallen (20th Anniversary Edition) offers newly remastered audio, including the album‚Äôs singles ‚ÄúMy Immortal,‚Äù ‚ÄúGoing Under,‚Äù ‚ÄúEverybody‚Äôs Fool,‚Äù and ‚ÄúBring Me To Life.‚Äù The expanded set also includes a trove of bonus material ‚Äì ten tracks in all ‚Äì comprising previously-unreleased demos and live recordings plus a selection of rare B-sides. Alongside reimagined artwork, all physical formats will include previously-unseen photos from the era, plus a handwritten foreword by Amy Lee, who oversaw all aspects of the reissue. The Deluxe vinyl, CD and digital configurations are out now. 

Available exclusively at Evanescence.com is the Super Deluxe Box Set, arriving February, 2024. Housed in a collectible shadow box-style package (inspired by Amy‚Äôs songwriting journal cover art), this limited edition includes all of the above-mentioned music as part of a 2-LP set (featuring a Black & Silver blend vinyl) plus a bonus cassette of previously unreleased demos and voice notes which is exclusive to this box set. Adding additional insight into the album is an expansive book which features new track-by-track notes from Lee, while a zoetropic turntable slipmat, rare photo prints, and enamel pin set round out the collection.

title: No One Noticed This About the K-Pop Demon Hunters Songs.. üòàü§î #music  #kpop
description:
So many people keep calling the music in KPop Demon Hunters generic, but most don‚Äôt realize there‚Äôs something hidden in each of the songs that proves they‚Äôre not as basic as they might seem. Beneath the surface, the soundtrack is packed with clever details, subtle callbacks, and even mistakes that turned into genius moments.

Take Soda Pop by the Saja Boys ‚Äî the vocals suddenly disappear to reveal that ‚ÄúBaby Saja‚Äù is rapping over a literal nursery rhyme, I‚Äôm a Little Teapot. Then there‚Äôs Golden by Huntr/x, which doesn‚Äôt just stand alone as a song, but actually appears in multiple variations across the entire movie‚Äôs soundtrack, weaving itself into the film‚Äôs musical DNA.

But the two cleverest hidden moments both come from another Huntr/x track. At first, you hear the lyric ‚ÄúI see your real face and it‚Äôs ugly as sin,‚Äù which sounds like a throwaway mistake ‚Äî but in reality, it‚Äôs Mira accidentally singing Zoey‚Äôs line. This small slip makes perfect sense once you realize that both characters are demons in disguise. And speaking of demons, there‚Äôs a reason why Rumi‚Äôs delivery of ‚ÄúA demon with no feelings don‚Äôt deserve to live‚Äù was changed from the studio version to the one used in the movie ‚Äî a change that carries much deeper meaning than you might expect.

I focus on trending topics or stories related to the singers and celebrities my audience loves, such as Taylor Swift, Olivia Rodrigo, and BLACKPINK. This involves researching their latest updates, analyzing fan responses, and selecting the most engaging angle. This step takes around 25 minutes and sets the tone for the entire project.
2. Gathering Clips and Editing (40 Minutes per Segment) Once the idea is finalized, I move on to collecting the necessary footage. This includes official clips, interviews, and fan-captured moments. I carefully trim and organize these clips to match the narrative. Each segment of the video is meticulously edited, with effects, transitions, and text overlays added to enhance the visual appeal. This step is time-intensive, with each section taking about 40 minutes to perfect.
3. Final Review and Adjustments (20 Minutes) After editing, I review the entire video to ensure smooth transitions and consistent pacing. During this phase, I also add voiceovers to provide context and commentary, ensuring the video aligns with my audience‚Äôs preferences. Any last-minute tweaks, like adjusting audio levels or refining effects, are made before the final export. This step takes approximately 20 minutes, wrapping up my editing process.

The official YouTube channel of Atlantic Records artist Kehlani.

It doesn‚Äôt really need an explanation‚Äîyou know exactly what Kehlani means when she sings. Without sugarcoating or softening a word, the Bay Area-born two-time GRAMMY¬Æ Award-nominated multiplatinum songstress will drop a hard truth in one breath and flip a middle finger in the next. She may extend a seductive invitation or an empathetic plea before leaving you in your thoughts and feelings. Either way, she finds a way to consistently relate without filter. With each move, she strengthens this connection to listeners everywhere.  Kehlani‚Äôs 2015 breakout mixtape You Should Be Here received a 2016 GRAMMY¬Æ Award nod in the category of ‚ÄúBest Urban Contemporary Album.‚Äù On its heels, her 2017 full-length debut SweetSexySavage bowed at #3 on the Billboard Top 200 and eventually went gold. Between selling out dates on the SweetSexySavage Tour, the record closed out the year on Pitchfork‚Äôs ‚ÄúThe 50 Best Albums of 2017‚Äù and Rolling Stone‚Äôs ‚Äú20 Best R&B Albums of 2017.‚Äù 

Along the way, she contributed to Suicide Squad: The Album and The Fate of the Furious: The Album and guested on Cardi B‚Äôs double-platinum ‚ÄúRing,‚Äù Kyle‚Äôs platinum ‚ÄúPLAYINWITME,‚Äù and Justin Bieber‚Äôs ‚ÄúGet Me,‚Äù to name a few. By 2020, she picked up three gold solo singles‚Äî"You Should Be Here,‚Äù ‚ÄúHoney,‚Äù and ‚ÄúDistraction,‚Äù for which she received her second GRAMMY¬Æ nomination for Best R&B performance. In addition, four platinum singles‚Äî‚ÄúGangsta,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Way‚Äù [feat. Chance the Rapper], ‚ÄúCRZY,‚Äù and ‚ÄúNights Like This‚Äù [feat. Ty Dolla $ign] and streams in the billions. Not to mention, Billboard Women In Music honored her with the ‚ÄúRule Breaker Award‚Äù as she gathered nominations at the Soul Train Awards and the American Music Awards. Plus, she made show-stopping appearances at Voodoo Music + More, Coachella, and beyond. In the aftermath of 2019‚Äôs chart-topping While We Wait mixtape, everything changed. She became a mom. As such, parenthood left an indelible imprint on her second full-length, It Was Good Until It Wasn‚Äôt. title: Believer Music Video! Sung by the Fun Squad (Imagine Dragons Cover)
description:
Believer Music Video! Sung by the Fun Squad (Imagine Dragons Cover) Fun Squad Studios and the @ImagineDragons charity, TRF @trfdotorg, team up to share the fight against pediatric cancer through the eyes of a survivor.  The story is uniquely told through music video, as the Fun Squad Studios musician teens, Jack, Jazzy and Kade Skye, sing a cover of the Imagine Dragons‚Äô song, Believer in a captivating depiction of real-life courage and bravery, Averi of @OurFantasticFive .

OUR GOAL: Help us raise $100K for kids with cancer and hit 5M views of AWARENESS for TRF! What can you do? SHARE THE VIDEO and DONATE! The mission of TRF is to strengthen families financially and emotionally as they cope with the tragedy of a pediatric cancer diagnosis by offsetting out-of-pocket life expenses. Find out more at TRF.org or https://www.youtube.com/@TylerRobinsonFoundation

description:
Believer Music Video! Sung by the Fun Squad (Imagine Dragons Cover) Fun Squad Studios and the @ImagineDragons charity, TRF @trfdotorg, team up to share the fight against pediatric cancer through the eyes of a survivor.  The story is uniquely told through music video, as the Fun Squad Studios musician teens, Jack, Jazzy and Kade Skye, sing a cover of the Imagine Dragons‚Äô song, Believer in a captivating depiction of real-life courage and bravery, Averi of @OurFantasticFive .

OUR GOAL: Help us raise $100K for kids with cancer and hit 5M views of AWARENESS for TRF! What can you do? SHARE THE VIDEO and DONATE! The mission of TRF is to strengthen families financially and emotionally as they cope with the tragedy of a pediatric cancer diagnosis by offsetting out-of-pocket life expenses. My Editing Process
1. Finding the Idea and Content (25 Minutes) The first step in my editing process is brainstorming and deciding on a video idea. I focus on trending topics or stories related to the singers and celebrities my audience loves, such as Taylor Swift, Olivia Rodrigo, and BLACKPINK. This involves researching their latest updates, analyzing fan responses, and selecting the most engaging angle. This step takes around 25 minutes and sets the tone for the entire project.
2. Gathering Clips and Editing (40 Minutes per Segment) Once the idea is finalized, I move on to collecting the necessary footage. This includes official clips, interviews, and fan-captured moments. I carefully trim and organize these clips to match the narrative. Each segment of the video is meticulously edited, with effects, transitions, and text overlays added to enhance the visual appeal. This step is time-intensive, with each section taking about 40 minutes to perfect.
3. Final Review and Adjustments (20 Minutes) After editing, I review the entire video to ensure smooth transitions and consistent pacing. During this phase, I also add voiceovers to provide context and commentary, ensuring the video aligns with my audience‚Äôs preferences. Any last-minute tweaks, like adjusting audio levels or refining effects, are made before the final export. This step takes approximately 20 minutes, wrapping up my editing process.

title: Neo Soul Music's Big Bang
description:
#bass #basshistory #groove #transcription #analysis #neosoul #paulthompson    
Celebrating one of the great musical debuts of the past 30 years, I'm digging deep into D'Angelo's 1995 debut album: BROWN SUGAR (EMI). I'll go track-by-track and dissect each bass line (and beat) and show you how D'Angelo created genius music from the bottom up--and not only on the keyboard bass, but also when he collaborated with great bass players like Larry Grenadier, Will Lee, and Raphael Saadiq. 

I'm digging into the  music, the stories, and I'll also show you EXACTLY how to play the hit bass line from "Lady" the right way! Don't miss my tribute to one of my favorite musicians, ever.

My preferred stem splitter: https://www.lalal.ai/?fp_ref=paul24

title: Moha Jadu | Coke Studio Bangla | Season 3 | Habib Wahid X Mehrnigori Rustam
description:
A mesmerizing blend of Bangla mysticism and Farsi poetry, where love becomes a force that moves the heart and pulls the soul like an unseen thread. #MohaJadu celebrates this love‚Äôs enchantment. 
Penned by the mystical poet Khoyaj Mia, a disciple of the revered mystic guide Durbin Shah, the song was born out of surrender, a seeker‚Äôs devotion to his murshid. Habib Wahid‚Äôs modern reinterpretation, paired with the voice of Mehrnigori Rustam, gives these timeless verses a fresh rhythm, vibrant, upbeat, and captivating.
Wrapped in melodies, it bridges time and culture, speaks of longing and surrender, and transcends unseen borders, where Bangla meets Farsi, and devotion finds a shared language. It carries with it both the #RealMagic of old mystic verses and the voice of a new generation listening in.

title: Chhaina Ra Maya - Prakash Dutraj | Melina Rai | Anjali GC | New Nepali Song 2082
description:
The Scene and characters shown in this song were filmed in Tetang village, located in the Mustang district at an altitude of approximately 3,040 meters above sea level. Mustang is a district blessed with breathtaking natural beauty. Cold winds, villages nested at the foothills of the Himalayas. 

The production of apples, potatoes, buckwheat, and wool, along with the salt mines, soda water springs, highland pastures, and yak caravans. 

These are the beautiful gifts nature has bestowed upon this land.

Titang village, located in the Mustang district, is a village rich in diverse art, culture, and natural beauty, around 25 to 30 years ago, the people living in this village used to trade locally produced goods and natural resources such as apples, potatoes, buckwheat, wool, and salt with other villages and even as far as Tibet.

We are grateful to all the fathers, mothers, brothers, and sisters residing in Tetang village of Mustang district. The video has been filmed based on such stories and the surrounding environment. Please accept it for you - it's for you.

description:

Turns out rainy days aren‚Äôt just for sad montages and soggy socks. Sometimes they make for perfect days. This mix is for those moments when the weather‚Äôs doing its thing and you‚Äôre just trying to do yours, whether it's working, thinking, spiraling slightly, or all three at once.

We carefully put together a bunch of tracks to listen to while you write emails you don‚Äôt want to send, stare out the window like you‚Äôre in an indie film, or just try to keep your brain from doing too much. Embrace the Rain isn‚Äôt about turning a gray day into sunshine. It‚Äôs about making space for the gray to be okay.

We hope this mix makes your day feel a little more doable. Or at least gives your brain a softer surface to land on. Thanks for listening.

Cody Johnson has established a following of passionately loyal fans who regularly sell out shows across the country. The artist that media has touted ‚Äújust might be the future of real country music‚Äù has skyrocketed success with numerous celebrated albums: Leather Deluxe Edition, Leather, Human The Double Album, A Cody Johnson Christmas, Cody Johnson & The Rockin‚Äô CJB Live, and Ain‚Äôt Nothin‚Äô To It plus an award-winning feature-length documentary ‚ÄúDear Rodeo: The Cody Johnson Story.‚Äù Cody has 42 Gold and Platinum certifications, nearly 10 Billion career global streams and four #1 singles. 
 
Cody‚Äôs #1 single ‚ÄúDirt Cheap,‚Äù written by Josh Philips, was awarded as Storyteller of The Year at the ‚ÄúPeople‚Äôs Choice Country Awards‚Äù and ‚ÄúThe Painter‚Äù was awarded as the NSAI 2024 Song of The Year for writers Benjy Davis, Kat Higgins and Ryan Larkins. Both #1 hits are included on Cody‚Äôs current album Leather Deluxe Edition.  
 
His numerous industry honors include recognition as a CMT Artist of The Year, two ACM Awards, three CMT Music Awards wins, four CMA Awards including Album of The Year (2024) for Leather, and being named ‚ÄúBest New Country Artist‚Äù at the iHeart Music and recognized with the Spirit award at the 2025 ACM Honors event. His television appearances have entertained fans on the Today Show, the Kelly Clarkson Show and the Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon in addition to outstanding live tv performances at the iHeart Music Awards, the ACM Awards, CMA Awards, CMT Music Awards, CMT Giants honoring Vince Gill, and the CMT Artist of the Year Special and more. Cody co-hosted the three-hour ‚ÄúCMA Fest Presented by Sofi‚Äù with Ashley McBryde this summer.

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films‚Äô Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story‚Ä¶and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question‚Ä¶do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

title: INSANE Illusion in ‚ÄúGolden‚Äù from K-Pop Demon Hunters üòàü§î #music #kpop
description:
What if I told you that one of the songs in KPop Demon Hunters hides one of the most insane audio illusions I‚Äôve ever heard ‚Äî and almost nobody noticed? The track Golden by Huntr/x (Rumi, Mira and Zoey) has a deceptively simple intro that has left listeners completely divided. Some swear it plays at the exact same speed and rhythm as the rest of the song, while others insist it feels slower, almost like a different time signature entirely.
In this breakdown, I‚Äôll show you both versions ‚Äî Option A in 12/8 and Option B in 3/4 ‚Äî and prove that your brain can actually switch between them depending on which drum pattern you heard last. It‚Äôs the kind of auditory trick that makes you question how you even hear rhythm in the first place.

Join me as we uncover this hidden illusion inside Huntr/x‚Äôs Golden, a song that proves the KPop Demon Hunters soundtrack is full of way more surprises than anyone expected.

Huntrix don‚Äôt quit how it‚Äôs done done done. We‚Äôre going up up up it‚Äôs our moment.

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films‚Äô Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story‚Ä¶and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question‚Ä¶do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

title: Chhaina Ra Maya - Prakash Dutraj | Melina Rai | Anjali GC | New Nepali Song 2082
description:
The Scene and characters shown in this song were filmed in Tetang village, located in the Mustang district at an altitude of approximately 3,040 meters above sea level. Mustang is a district blessed with breathtaking natural beauty. Cold winds, villages nested at the foothills of the Himalayas. 

The production of apples, potatoes, buckwheat, and wool, along with the salt mines, soda water springs, highland pastures, and yak caravans. 

These are the beautiful gifts nature has bestowed upon this land.

Titang village, located in the Mustang district, is a village rich in diverse art, culture, and natural beauty, around 25 to 30 years ago, the people living in this village used to trade locally produced goods and natural resources such as apples, potatoes, buckwheat, wool, and salt with other villages and even as far as Tibet.

We are grateful to all the fathers, mothers, brothers, and sisters residing in Tetang village of Mustang district. The video has been filmed based on such stories and the surrounding environment. Please accept it for you - it's for you.

An emotionally charged composition by Darshan Raval that delves deep into the turmoil of anger, betrayal, and heartbreak. It expresses the raw pain of trusting someone who ends up breaking that very trust, leaving behind scars that never fade. Sung and composed by Darshan Raval, with heartfelt lyrics by Noor, the song beautifully blends emotion and melody to portray the darker side of love. What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

title: Age of Apes ads review new level: Lead your monkeys #games #gaming #funny
#shorts GLASS Planets | Planet SIZES for BABY | Funny Planet comparison Game for kids | 8 Planets
description:
#atoyday #shorts #planetcomparison #planetsize #planetforbaby #solarsystemsize #planetforkid 
Watch full video: https://youtu.be/6X5g3z325b4
Enjoy #shorts of this simple funny educational video helps to imagine sizes of our planets for kids of all ages.  You will see WHITE GLASS planets and try to guess the planet. Just in a second small helpers come and break the glass to find out what planet is under it. Meet our funny helpers: a hammer, a shovel , a rake, a baseball bat, and others. Kids can help to find the corresponding planet. Let's learn and compare 8 Planets of the Solar System. 
The smallest planet in the Solar System is Mercury, next one in size is Mars, Venus is much bigger, our Earth is almost the same size, next one is a giant Neptune, Uranus is a little bigger, then Saturn, and biggest planet of the Solar System is Jupiter. However all the planets are small babies when you see how huge the Sun is!
Excellent for the preschool, kindergarten or elementary school lessons.
Hope you can learn something new and at the same time smile when you watch our video! Enjoy and subscribe to watch more!  
How to learn the order of the planets? 
Just remember:
My                 Mercury
Very               Venus
Educated       Earth
Mom               Mars
Just                Jupiter
Served            Saturn
Us                    Uranus
Nachos           Neptune

But where is Pluto? Pluto is a dwarf planet in the Kuiper belt, a ring of bodies beyond Neptune. Pluto was discovered by Clyde Tombaugh in 1930 and was originally considered to be the ninth planet from the Sun. Pluto is very small, only about half the width of the United States, that's the main reason why Pluto was relegated to "dwarf-planet" status by the International Astronomical Union in 2006.

title: Vince McMahon will have crash charges dropped after probation program | News 12
description:
A judge granted a pre-trial probation program to former WWE CEO Vince McMahon, which will allow the charges in his reckless driving case to be dropped in one year. When McMahon arrived at Stamford Superior Court, he was met by a group of fans, waiting out front, in hopes of getting a picture of autograph. McMahon paused by them briefly before walking in surrounded by his security team. The hearing came several weeks after McMahon applied for a program called accelerated rehabilitation in connection with a three-car crash on the Merritt Parkway in Westport. According to the police report, on July 24, McMahon drove his Bentley into the back of a BMW, then the center median, with debris from the collision causing another vehicle to crash. No one was hurt, but McMahon was charged with reckless driving and following too closely. It happened just hours before Hulk Hogan's death became public.

title: ABC World News Tonight with David Muir Full Broadcast - Oct. 5, 2025
description:
Selina Wang reports the White House is now sending California National Guard troops to Portland after a federal judge temporarily blocked the administration's attempt to federalize and deploy the Oregon National Guard; Ian Pannell is in Jerusalem on the eve of those critical ceasefire talks between delegations of Hamas and Israel in Egypt; with congressional leaders still at odds over the government shutdown, Alex Presha explains why each side blames the other for the impasse; Reena Roy has more on the former NFL quarterback who is now facing multiple criminal charges; and more on tonight‚Äôs broadcast of World News Tonight with David Muir.

In Tel Aviv, David Muir reports on the historic day in the Middle East after Hamas freed the surviving hostages, and Israel released nearly 2,000 Palestinian prisoners; Matt Rivers has details on the powerful nor'easter that turned deadly when a 76-year-old woman in New York City was killed after a gust of wind knocked down a solar panel and hit her; Rachel Scott has the latest on the government shutdown; and more on tonight‚Äôs broadcast of World News Tonight with David Muir reporting from Israel.

title: ABC World News Tonight with David Muir Full Broadcast - Oct. 7, 2025
description:
On the seventh day of the government shutdown, Gio Benitez has the latest on the FAA warning about staffing shortages at major hubs such as Newark, Houston, Chicago and Las Vegas after air traffic controllers call out sick during the government shutdown; Rachel Scott reports on Pres. Trump suggesting that some of the 750,000 federal workers currently furloughed without pay may not get back pay when the government reopens; Matt Gutman has details on the medical helicopter carrying three people that crashed onto a busy highway in Sacramento, California, shutting down traffic; and more on tonight‚Äôs broadcast of World News Tonight with David Muir.

title: ABC World News Tonight with David Muir Full Broadcast - Oct. 6, 2025
description:
Matt Rivers has the latest on former NFL quarterback Mark Sanchez, who is recovering in the hospital and facing a felony battery charge after allegedly injured a delivery truck driver during a physical altercation; as the government shutdown drags into its sixth day with no end in sight, Jay O‚ÄôBrien has details on the millions of federal employees ‚Äì such as air traffic controllers ‚Äì worrying about missing paycheck during the government shutdown, while Congress still gets theirs; Rachel Scott has the latest on Illinois and the city of Chicago and filing a lawsuit to block Pres. Trump‚Äôs deployment of National Guard in Chicago; and more on tonight‚Äôs broadcast of World News Tonight with David Muir.

00:00 Intro 
02:34 Former NFL star Mark Sanchez charged with felony after fight, faces up to 6 years in prison if convicted
05:26 Air traffic controllers forced to work without pay as government shutdown enters 6th day
07:34 Illinois governor, city of Chicago sue to block Trump's deployment of National Guard
10:15 SCOTUS rejects Ghislaine Maxwell's appeal on sex trafficking charges
12:24 Fire destroys South Carolina judge's waterfront home, injures 3
13:37 Israel-Hamas truce talks underway in Egypt on eve of second anniversary of October 7 attack
14:50 Urgent rescue underway for hikers stranded on Mount Everest after blizzard

17:16 Video shows moment elephant charges tourists on Botswana safari

title: Caught on camera: 15-year-old driver hits pedestrian in East New York crash | News 12
description:

The driver ran from the scene seemingly uninjured.

title: Same man arrested in violent Bronx attacks on nurse's aide, teenager | News 12
description:
Police say they have a suspect in custody for two violent attacks across The Bronx. Police say they arrested 23-year-old Jeremiah White for attacking nurse's aide Virginia Alvarez, a BronxCare Health employee on her way to work. Marissa Santorelli spoke exclusively with the health care worker's mother. Police also connected White to an attack on a teenage girl in Crotona Park East. The teenager was found by police with injuries to her head and taken to Jacobi Hospital. White is charged with second-degree assault causing a serious physical injury in the attack on the teen, which is a felony.

The DUCSU elections were held amidst various expectations, fears and realities. A month has passed since the elections. During the elections, the leaders made a lot of promises. Some of their work has been visible in the first month. DUCSU leaders have alleged that the university administration is not cooperating with the committee. A day after the results of the DUCSU elections were announced, the Chittagong University premises have been completely quiet since morning. Since the educational institutions were closed, there was a deafening silence on the campus except for a few residential students. As per the expectations of the students, the newly elected leaders will soon start working to solve various problems including the housing crisis and stopping cyberbullying, as per the manifesto.

title: Kongresista may P500-M insertion sa PNP? | ABS-CBN News
description:
Ibinunyag ni Department of Interior and Local Government (DILG) Secretary Jonvic Remulla na ibinalik ng Philippine National Police (PNP) sa Office of the President ang P500-milyon mula sa P1.3-bilyong intelligence fund nito para sa 2025 matapos matuklasang ito ay "insertion" umano ng isang kongresista.

Sa pagdinig ng Senado para sa budget ng DILG nitong Huwebes (Oktubre 16), sinabi ni Remulla na ang kongresista ay pareho sa mambabatas na nanghingi umano ng import permits sa Department of Agriculture para sa 3,000 container ng isda para sa tatlong kumpanya.

‚ÄúWe returned it because it was an insertion in the budget and the insertion came from the person who requested 3,000 containers of fish,‚Äù ani Remulla.

Walang ibinigay na pangalan si Remulla ngunit matatandaang ibinunyag ni DA Secretary Francisco Tiu Laurel noong Setyembre 16 sa Senado na sinubukang manghingi ni dating Ako Bicol Rep. Zaldy Co ng import permits para sa parehong dami ng container ng isda.

title: Same man arrested in violent Bronx attacks on nurse's aide, teenager | News 12
description:
Police say they have a suspect in custody for two violent attacks across The Bronx. Police say they arrested 23-year-old Jeremiah White for attacking nurse's aide Virginia Alvarez, a BronxCare Health employee on her way to work. Marissa Santorelli spoke exclusively with the health care worker's mother. Police also connected White to an attack on a teenage girl in Crotona Park East. The teenager was found by police with injuries to her head and taken to Jacobi Hospital. White is charged with second-degree assault causing a serious physical injury in the attack on the teen, which is a felony.

title: Assam: Protest erupts in Baksa over transfer of Zubeen Garg case accused to newly constructed prison
description:
Click here https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC3zMA8hCzeB8ldnFVGX1NFA/join and  ‚ÄòJoin‚Äô  to become a part of the EastMojo family today!

Scores of people took to the streets of Baksa district in Assam after the five people arrested in connection with the death of singer Zubeen Garg were shifted to the district jail on October 15.

The situation outside the jail in Mushalpur remained tense as fans threw stones and tried to enter the premises. Protestors even set several vehicles ablaze following which police resorted to lathi-charging and firing teargas shells. Several shots were also fired to disperse the crowd but the situation could not be brought under control. As per reports, several reporters on the spot, police officers and protestors suffered injuries during the scuffle. The exact number of those injured and damage to property could not be ascertained at the time of filing this report. 

Protesters, earlier said they were unhappy with the decision to send the accused to Baksa Jail, which is a newly constructed facility with no inmates and modern amenities. They also alleged that the state government was trying to protect the accused.

The development comes after five accused ‚ÄîShyamkanu Mahanta the chief organiser of North East India Festival, Zubeen‚Äôs manager Siddhartha Sharma, his cousin and police officer Sandipan Garg, and his two personal security officers Nandeswar Bora and Prabin Baishya ‚Äî were sent to judicial custody by the Kamrup Chief Judicial Magistrate on Wednesday.

The court, citing concerns for their safety, directed that they be lodged in a jail with fewer inmates. Following the order, the authorities decided to shift all five to the newly inaugurated Baksa District Jail in Mushalpur, which currently has no prisoners.

title: Saksi Express: October 15, 2025 [HD]
description:
Narito ang mga balitang ating sinaksihan ngayong Miyerkules October 15, 2025.




- Iloilo, niyanig ng magnitude 4.2 na lindol; klase mula kinder hanggang shs at trabaho sa kapitolyo, sinuspinde


- 900 pamilya, nasunugan


- Pasaporte nina Ex-PCSO GM Garma, Ex-NAPOLCOM Comm. Leonardo at 3 iba pa, pinakakansela ng korte; hold departure order laban sa kanila, inilabas din


- Super health center sa Marikina, noong 2024 pa naitayo ang pundasyon pero nakatengga ang konstruksyon hanggang ngayon


- Iba't ibang ilegal na armas at P400,000 halaga ng shabu, nakumpiska; suspek, arestado


- Mag-asawang Discaya, hindi na makikipagtulungan sa imbestigasyon ng ICI


- Presyo ng itlog sa ilang pamilihan, tumaas


- 64 patay, 65 nawawala dahil sa matinding pagbaha at landslide sa Mexico


- Sinisanteng pump boy attendant, nang-holdap sa gasolinahan; mahigit P100,000, natangay


- Binabantayang LPA, posibleng pumasok bukas sa PAR


- Mariah Carey, kinanta ang "All I Want for Christmas is You" bilang finale sa kanyang concert kagabi

The Toshakhana of the Banke Bihari Temple in Vrindavan was built in 1862. Its creator was Goswami Jagannathji, a disciple of Haridas Maharaj. Its location was decided to be Vrindavan, the city of Krishna. Its purpose was to collect a treasure trove of precious and valuable offerings. Its management remained in the hands of the Goswami family.

title: 24 Oras Express: October 16, 2025 [HD]
description:
Narito ang mga maiinit na balita sa 24 Oras Express ngayong Huwebes, October 16, 2025.


- Ombudsman: Pinoprotektahan ng mga Discaya si Sen. Go, may joint venture ang mga pamilya nila

- Sen. Go sa alegasyong pinoprotektahan siya ng mga Discaya: 'Wag tayong lumihis at panagutin ang dapat managot

- VP Duterte, may hinalang iuugnay sila ni Ex-Pres. Duterte sa flood control controversy kasunod ng imbestigasyon sa kumpanya ng pamilya ni Sen. Go

- Palasyo, sinabing kumpiyansa ang isang tao kung ang ginagawa ay 'di para sa pansariling interes

- Rehabilitasyon sa tulay sa Laur, Nueva Ecija, ipinagpaliban ng DPWH sa Nobyembre matapos tutulan ng mga residente

- Nakaparadang SUV, sinilaban ng 'di pa nakikilalang salarin

- DOH, kinuwestyon kung bakit kabubukas lang ang center na July 2024 pa natapos; LGU: hinanapan pa ito ng staff

- Driver ng pickup na naka-diplomatic plate, tinutugis matapos takasan ang binanggang rider na may angkas na bata

- Mga negosyong may kinalaman sa turismo, umaapela ng tulong dahil sa matumal na kita mula nang lumindol

- Mga suspek na sumugod sa bahay at nanakit, sinampahan na ng reklamo; pakay ang 13-anyos umanong nobya ng 30-anyos na suspek

- Rep. Leviste: Ilang appointee sa DPWH, contractor o may koneksyon sa contractor ayon sa kanyang source

- M4.7 na lindol, yumanig sa Zambales; naramdaman din sa Tarlac at Bataan

- Pagbawi sa perang ninakaw sa maanomalyang flood control projects, pinaguusapan na ng ICI

- Guro, binaril ng mister sa paaralan

- Bahagi ng A. Bonifacio St., may palatandaang dinadaanan ito ng West Valley Fault

- Low Pressure Area sa Philippine Area of Responsibility, posible nang maging bagyo anumang oras ngayon

- Ogie Alcasid, Vice Ganda, atbp., mapapanood sa part2 ng anniversary special ng 'Bubble Gang'

- Sec. Remulla: May P500M insertion sa intel funds ng PNP Ngayong 2025; pondo, isinauli sa Office of the Pres.

- Pamamahagi ng P3,000 e-voucher na pambili ng pagkain kada buwan, pinalawig

- Ruru Madrid, abala sa pagsasanay ng Pinoy Martial Arts na 'Laraw Kali Pamuok'

- Luxury car na sinita dahil walang plaka, galing sa importer kung saan binili ang mga sasakyan ng mga Discaya

- 3 Koreanong wanted sa kanilang bansa dahil sa loan fraud scheme, arestado

- Namataang istruktura sa Bajo De Masinloc, lumabas na AFP ang nagtayo noong 1990s

- 'My Father's Wife' cast, nakisaya sa Coramblan Fest; tinikman din ang mga lutong Alaminos

- Ex-PNP Chief Acorda, itinalagang bagong Executive Director ng PAOCC

- Asong nahulog sa sink hole, buwis-buhay na sinagip ng ilang residente

- Pokwang, iginiit na 'di siya nag-eendorso ng sugal gaya nang gustong palabasin sa deepfake video

title: Assam CM clarifies reason for providing security to Singapore NRIs during CID summons
description:
Assam Chief Minister Himanta Biswa Sarma on October 15 clarified the reason for providing security to the Singapore NRIs during CID summons in Guwahati. He further said the NRIs from Singapore who were summoned by the CID are friends of late singer Zubeen Garg and ‚Äúbright Assamese individuals‚Äù representing the state abroad. 

He explained that security was provided to them as a precautionary measure. Referring to the Baksa incident, the Chief Minister said, ‚ÄúWhat if something similar had happened at the CID office? Who would have taken responsibility? If such incidents occurred, people would hesitate to come to Assam."

title: TV Patrol Playback | October 16, 2025
description:
Narito ang mga Balita mula sa TV Patrol ngayong Oktubre 16, 2025.

0:00:00 - Intro

0:34:02 - ABS-CBN News Campus Patrol, bumisita sa University of Asia and the Pacific

title: Peru to declare state of emergency over protests | BBC News
description:
The government of Peru is to declare a state of emergency in the capital Lima following widespread clashes between protesters and riot police.
 
The protests have left a 32-year-old man dead and more than 100 people injured, including many police officers.
 
Wednesday's demonstrations were organised by mainly young Peruvians who demand that the country's political class do more to combat high levels of crime and corruption.
 
President Jer√≠ said the protest had been infiltrated by criminals set on causing chaos and launched an investigation into the circumstances surrounding the protester's death.

A horrific road accident happened in Delhi Cantt area on Sunday afternoon. It is said that a speeding BMW car hit a couple riding a bike. Deputy Secretary Navjot Singh posted in the Finance Ministry was returning to his house in Janakpuri with his wife on the bike. Navjot Singh died in the accident. The speed of the car was so high that after hitting Navjot Singh's bike, it lost its balance and overturned and hit the divider.

title: Bihar news live news today of 10th October 2025.BTSC Vacancy,Bihar Assembly elections 2025.
description:
Bihar news live news today of 10th october 2025.Bihar assembly elections 2025,Bihar weather today,BTSC Vacancy, Patna Junction, Surendra jha suman birthday
#biharnews #biharnewslive #biharnewstoday #biharkesamachar #bihartouristplaces #biharvacancy #Biharelections2025 #currentaffairsbihars #biharweather #biharkaaajkhabar 
1. Apply today for 4,654 BTSC positions

The Bihar Technical Services Commission #BTSCvacancy has announced recruitment for a total of 4,654 positions for Work Inspectors, Hostel Managers, Dental Hygienists, and Junior Engineers. The recruitment process includes 2,747 Junior Engineer (Civil/Electrical/Mechanical) positions, 1,114 Work Inspector positions, 91 Hostel Manager positions, and 702 Dental Hygienists. Applications will open on October 10, 2025, and can be submitted through November 10, 2025, at btsc.bihar.gov.in. The age limit is 18-37 years (varying by position). Hostel Managers require a B.Sc./Hotel Management Diploma, Work Inspectors require a Matriculation + ITI, and Dental Hygienists require a 10+2 + 2-year Diploma. The pay scale is in accordance with the Seventh Pay Commission.
2. Nominations for the first phase of Bihar Assembly elections begin today.

3. Learn the significance of #KarvachauthSargi and the correct method of observing the fast.

Married women observe the Karva Chauth fast on the Chaturthi (fourth day) of the Krishna Paksha (dark fortnight) of Kartik month by observing a waterless fast for the long life of their husbands. The fast begins with the Sargi, which is eaten before sunrise and given by the mother-in-law to her daughter-in-law. This year, the Brahma Muhurta (time of Brahma Muhurta) is from 4:35 am to 5:23 am, and eating Sargi during this time is considered auspicious. Eating Sargi provides strength, stamina, and health. According to the ritual, bathe before sunrise, arrange the Sargi on a plate, remember Lord Shiva, Goddess Parvati, and Lord Chandra, and take a vow to observe the fast.
Before implementing any of the methods mentioned here, be sure to consult relevant experts.
4. Banana sales banned at #Patnajunction to maintain cleanliness.
5. Names can be added to the list up to 10 days before voting.

6. BSSC invites applications for 379 sports trainer positions by November 9th.

7. 8.5 lakh officers will be deployed for election security.

8. Data operator Satish Kumar caught red-handed accepting Rs 15,000.

9. The option to share earthquake alerts will soon be available on Android.
10. Today, in Bihari Birthday Special, we will talk about #Surendrajhasumanbirthday'.

11. Now, 85+ and disabled voters can cast their votes from home.
12. Khushboo Mishra, who misbehaved with a TTE, has been identified.

13. Sonakshi and Zaheer have purchased a new home in a posh area of ‚Äã‚ÄãMumbai.

14. Candidates are preparing for nominations keeping in mind omens and omens.

15. Find out what the weather will be like in #Biharweathertoday.

16. Munger police destroyed illegal liquor distilleries ahead of the elections.

17. Nityanand Rai dismissed rumors of Chirag Paswan's displeasure.

18. Tejashwi Yadav's big election promise: a government job for every household.

19. Jansuraj released the first list of 51 candidates for the Bihar elections.

20. Mohammed Shami broke his silence after being ruled out of the series against Australia.

21. Today's date is etched in Indian history for many reasons.

22. The explosive teaser of Huma Qureshi's 'Maharani 4' was released.

23. India's rapid rise in innovation, patents increased 100% in 10 years.

24. Learn the truth about the fake PIB Instagram account.

25. Apply for the UGC NET 2025 exam by November 7.

26. Vice President C.P. Radhakrishnan will visit Saran on October 11.
